To build a Docker image from the HXTool source, do the following:
1. Move the HXTool code to a folder called 'src'
2. Move/copy the Dockerfile to the directory above 'src'
3. Run 'docker build -t hxtool:latest .'

Your directory structure should look like so:

root
+---src
	\---hxtool source code
+---Dockerfile
